{"tid":1523754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過今晚 如果聽日都揸唔撚爆個春袋佢 後日都唔肯罷工","createTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T17:25:43.000Z","uid":116568,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8a32dbd5f255a86ec622717a23d6807370c358","tid":1523754,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F6kWNVw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF6kWNVw.jpg&h=64b2adaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢幅相<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><br />\n如果聽日都揸唔撚爆個春袋<br />\n<br />\n後日都唔肯罷工既話</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你諗下黑警港共係背後會點撚樣笑柒我地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你諗下今日班義士係前線承受水炮車 真槍實彈既威脅 佢地冇退縮過<br />\n<br />\n如果你地連和理非活動都唔參加<br />\n<br />\n香港將陷入白色恐怖既深淵 將會步新疆後塵<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以懇請大家今日出左既 聽日要繼續出<br />\n<br />\n今日冇去既 麻煩你聽日一定要出<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">記住</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有眼前路<br />\n沒有身後身</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c1a76975d9a483b773d3270a80d03f9d505f056f","tid":1523754,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:03.000Z","msg":"網絡大軍通宵推機場po"},{"pid":"0e1806b04e7a33ea18f865839a063ca5fc7fd998","tid":1523754,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:10:06.000Z","msg":"我要揸春袋<br />\n我要大罷工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f89c087cc53e0eb088df8cd097ef0475905abf6","tid":1523754,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike"